Next, I have to figure out the ward changes. I'm looking for "Xã Phước Minh" within the *new* province of Khánh Hòa. This requires checking through resolutions. This directly relates to the given address. I've got confirmation in the "New wards" list: {"ward_code":"22897","ward_name":"Xã Thuận Nam","province_name":"Tỉnh Khánh Hòa"}. This exactly matches what I found in the resolution.

Therefore, my final output will be constructed with high confidence, showing that "Xã Phước Minh" is now "Xã Thuận Nam," as per resolution 1667/NQ-UBTVQH15.
